Package org.jboss.windup.rules.apps.java.reporting.rules

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    UnparsablesAppReportModel
    Model of the Unparsable Files report.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    CreateAboutWindupReportRuleProvider
    Create a report HTML page about Windup.
    CreateCompatibleFileReportRuleProvider
    Creates the report HTML page for compatible files - "lift and shift" files.
    CreateDependencyGraphDataRuleProvider
    Generates a .js (javascript) file in the reports directory containing the apps and their dependencies.
    CreateDependencyGraphReportRuleProvider
    Generates the dependency graph reports for the applications analyzed
    CreateIssueSummaryDataRuleProvider
    Generates a .js (javascript) file in the reports directory with detailed issue summary information.
    CreateIssueSummaryDataRuleProvider.PropertyFilterMixin  
    CreateJavaApplicationOverviewReportRuleProvider
    Creates the main report HTML page for a Java application.
    CreateJavaIgnoredFilesReportRuleProvider
    Creates a report for all the ignored files along with all the regexes they were matched against.
    CreateReportIndexRuleProvider
    Creates a report with a list of other reports, as well as summary information about the analysis findings.
    CreateUnparsableFilesReportRuleProvider
    Creates the main report HTML page for a Java application.
    EnableCompatibleFilesReportOption
    Indicates that the compatible files report should be generated.
